    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to invoice.payment_term. Business justification: Semiconductor quotes specify payment terms that flow through to contracts and invoices. Linking quote to the canonical payment_term record enables quote-to-invoice terms consistency validation, suppor' ;
